description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 3, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 9, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Leverage for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70033-16464-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [9 Votes, Common]
